{
  "texts": [
    "Aside from the reproducibility limitations, the gENder-IT corpus does not contain any gender-neutral sentences (e.g.",
    "using the gender-neutral pronoun they in the English source).",
    "We prompted ChatGPT to generate gender alternatives but did not ask specifically for gender-neutral alternatives.",
    "While Ghosh and Caliskan (2023) finds that ChatGPT cannot handle the English gender-neutral pronoun, they also did not explicitly prompt it to translate in a gender-neutral way.",
    "In conclusion, this chapter has delved into the critical role of MT in perpetuating and shaping societal biases, particularly gender bias."
  ]
}